0.1 坐标轴标题带特殊字符且需换行

方法一：用ggtext

问题是：pdf版本的希腊字母显示异常

library(ggtext) 
p <- ggplot(mpg, aes(displ, hwy))+
  geom_point()+
  theme(axis.title.x = element_markdown(),
        axis.title.y = element_markdown())+
  xlab("N<sub>2</sub> fixation rate<br> (nmol N &mu;g^-1 Chl*a* h<sup>-1</sup>)")+
  ylab("Dissolved <sup>113</sup>Cd <br>(&mu;g L<sup>-1</sup>)")

p

ggsave("test.1.pdf") # 希腊字母显示异常

cairo_pdf("test.2.pdf") # 希腊字母显示正常，注意，Mac电脑需先安装XQuartz（https://www.xquartz.org/）才能正常使用此功能
p
dev.off()
## quartz_off_screen 
##                 2

参考：https://github.com/wilkelab/ggtext/issues/1 https://stackoverflow.com/questions/38952427/include-cairo-r-on-a-mac

方法二：用atop
问题是：行距偏大

ggplot(mpg, aes(displ, hwy))+
  geom_point()+
  
  xlab(~atop(N[2]~"fixation rate", "(nmol N"~mu*g^{-1}~"Chl"*italic(a)~h^{-1}*")"))+
  ylab(~atop("Dissolved "^113*Cd, "("*mu*g~L^-1*")"))

0.2 更新部分数据，replace()函数

d_0 <- data.frame(plot=c('a', 'b', 'c', 'd'), 
                  sp1=c(100, 101, NA, NA),
                  sp2=4)
d_0
##   plot sp1 sp2
## 1    a 100   4
## 2    b 101   4
## 3    c  NA   4
## 4    d  NA   4
d_1 <- data.frame(plot=c('c', 'd'), sp1=c(200, 201))
d_1
##   plot sp1
## 1    c 200
## 2    d 201
d_0$sp1 <- replace(d_0$sp1, d_0$plot %in% d_1$plot, d_1$sp1)
d_0
##   plot sp1 sp2
## 1    a 100   4
## 2    b 101   4
## 3    c 200   4
## 4    d 201   4

0.3 加背景填充，区分不同阶段

d_shade <- data.frame(xmin=c(0,2,4,6,8,10),
                      xmax=c(2,4,6,8,10,12),
                      food=c("food","nofood","food","nofood","food","nofood"))

ggplot(ChickWeight, aes(Time, weight, group=Chick))+
  geom_line()+
  geom_point()+
  geom_rect(data=d_shade, aes(xmin=xmin, xmax=xmax, 
                           ymin=400, ymax=410, 
                           fill=food), color="transparent",
            inherit.aes = F)+
  geom_segment(data= d_shade, aes(x=xmin, xend=xmin, y=0, yend=400), 
               linetype="dotted", size=0.3,inherit.aes = F )

0.4 分别控制各个facet的刻度

library(ggh4x) #install.packages("ggh4x")

scales <- list(
  scale_x_reverse(),
  scale_x_continuous(labels = scales::dollar,
                     minor_breaks = c(2.5, 4.5)),
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(2.945, 6),
                     limits = c(0, 10),
                     guide = "axis_minor"))


ggplot(mpg, aes(displ, hwy)) + 
  geom_point()+
  facet_wrap(~drv, scales = "free_x") +
  facetted_pos_scales(x = scales)

参考：https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/ggh4x/vignettes/Facets.html

查看guide的用法：?guides

0.5 如何用facet_warp同时画多个不同y变量的图

library(tidyverse)

# Convert the original dataframe to long format
air_df <- airquality %>% pivot_longer(cols = 1:4, 
                                      names_to = "Env_vars", 
                                      values_to = "Values")

# Plot   
ggplot(air_df, aes(x = Day, y = Values, color = as.factor(Month), group = Month)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_line() +
  labs(x = "Day of month", y = NULL) +
  scale_color_brewer(palette = "Set1", 
                     labels = c("May", "June", "July", "August", "September")) +
  facet_wrap(~Env_vars, 
             nrow = 2, 
             scales = "free_y",
             strip.position = "left", 
             labeller = as_labeller(c(Temp = "Temperature (°F)", 
                                      Solar.R = "Solar radiace (lang)",
                                      Wind = "Wind (mph)",
                                      Ozone = "Ozone (ppb)"))) + 
  theme(strip.background = element_blank(),
        strip.placement = "outside",
        legend.position = "top",
        legend.title = element_blank())

Reference: https://genchanghsu.github.io/ggGallery/posts/2021-09-11-post-7-customize-the-axis-scales-for-individual-facets/

0.6 添加minor ticks

# library(ggh4x) 
p <- ggplot(iris, aes(Sepal.Width, Sepal.Length)) +
  geom_point()
p

p + scale_y_continuous(guide = "axis_minor")

# Minor break positions are still controlled by the scale
p + scale_y_continuous(guide = "axis_minor",
                       minor_breaks = seq(4, 8, by = 0.2))

0.7 画出每个facet的坐标轴

不因facet而丢失坐标轴，重复画出坐标轴。

library(lemon)

mpg |> 
  ggplot(aes(displ, hwy))+
  theme_classic()+
  geom_point()+
  facet_rep_wrap(~drv)+ # 类似地，有facet_rep_grid
  theme(strip.background = element_blank())

0.8 只在一个facet分面加logticks

## 定义函数
## 只在一个facet添加logtics
add_logticks  <- function (base = 10, sides = "bl", scaled = TRUE, 
                           short = unit(0.1, "cm"), mid = unit(0.2, "cm"),  long = unit(0.3, "cm"), 
                           colour = "black",  size = 0.5, linetype = 1, alpha = 1, color = NULL, 
                           data =data.frame(x = NA),... )   {
  if (!is.null(color)) 
    colour <- color
  layer(geom = "logticks", params = list(base = base, 
                                         sides = sides, scaled = scaled, short = short, 
                                         mid = mid, long = long, colour = colour, size = size, 
                                         linetype = linetype, alpha = alpha, ...), 
        stat = "identity", data = data , mapping = NULL, inherit.aes = FALSE, position = "identity",
        show.legend = FALSE)
}


mpg |> 
  ggplot(aes(displ, hwy))+
  theme_minimal()+
  geom_point()+
  facet_grid(factor(drv, levels = c("f","r","4"))~., )+ #重新排序，而不改变数据
  theme(axis.ticks.x = element_line(),
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank())+
  scale_x_log10()+
  add_logticks(sides = 'b', data = data.frame( drv = '4')) #在“drv = r”这个facet添加logticks

0.10 axis text 混合字体 上标下标斜体正体

labels <- c(expression('Sp.1,'~italic('virginica')), 
         expression('Sp.2,'~italic('versicolor')), 
         expression('Sp.3,'~italic('setosa')))


ggplot(iris, aes(Species, Petal.Length))+
  geom_point()+
  coord_flip()+
  scale_x_discrete(labels=labels)

0.11 双颜色系列

library(ggnewscale)
library(tidyverse)
library(ggsci)

ggplot()+
  geom_point(data=filter(mpg, hwy>25), aes(displ, hwy, color=drv))+
  scale_color_aaas()+
  labs(color="> 25")  +
    
  new_scale_colour() +
  geom_point(data=filter(mpg, hwy<25), aes(displ, hwy, color=drv))+
  scale_color_jco()+
  labs(color="< 25")

ref：https://gradientdescending.com/how-to-use-multiple-color-scales-in-ggplot-with-ggnewscale/

0.12 拓展作图区域，超出坐标轴范围

不需要拓展坐标轴范围，实现在范围外添加文字。

mpg |> 
  ggplot(aes(displ, hwy))+
  theme_classic()+
  geom_point()+
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(0, 8), clip = "off")+ # 取消裁剪
  theme(plot.margin = margin(r = 5, unit = "cm"))+ #增加右侧空白
  annotate(geom="text", x=10, y =30, label="test\ntext", lineheight = 0.7)

0.13 给每个facet添加inset

library(tidyverse)
library(ggpmisc)

## inset合并的图（大图）
pp_inset <- mpg |> 
  filter(displ>=5) |> 
  ggplot(aes(displ, cty))+
  theme_classic()+
  geom_point()+
  facet_wrap(~drv, ncol=1)+
  scale_y_continuous(position = "right")+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks=5:7)

pp_inset

# 制作inset单独的图（小图）
inset <- lapply(seq_len(3), function(i) { #此处数字3替换为实际的分面数
  pp_inset + 
    ggforce::facet_wrap_paginate(~ drv, nrow = 1, ncol = 1, page = i) +
   
    theme(strip.background = element_blank(),
          strip.text = element_blank(),
          #axis.title = element_blank(),
          plot.background = element_blank(),
          legend.position = "none")
})

inset 
## [[1]]

## 
## [[2]]

## 
## [[3]]

# 制作inset数据表
inset_tibble <- tibble(plot = inset,
                       drv = unique(mpg$drv))

inset_tibble
## # A tibble: 3 × 2
##   plot   drv  
##   <list> <chr>
## 1 <gg>   f    
## 2 <gg>   4    
## 3 <gg>   r
# 画图，插入inset
mpg |> 
  ggplot(aes(displ, hwy))+
  theme_classic()+
  geom_point()+
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(NA, 8), breaks=2:7)+
  facet_wrap(~drv, ncol=1)+
  geom_plot_npc(data = inset_tibble,
                aes(npcx = 1, npcy = 0.9, # inset插入位置
                    label = plot,  
                    vp.width = 0.4, vp.height = 0.6)) #inset尺寸

参考：https://stackoverflow.com/questions/62579733/produce-an-inset-in-each-facet-of-an-r-ggplot-while-preserving-colours-of-the-or
